data.description: Homesteader Ranchette!Approx 1363sf 3B/2B on approx 1.25ac of level usable land! Completely Rebuilt from the studs up! Quality Craftsmanship. Gorgeous Granite tops through out. Luxury vinyl flooring. Stunning Kitchen! Custom cabinetry- soft close, under cab lighting, stainless appliances. Spacious Living rm. Wheelchair accessible doors. Central HVAC. Oversized attached 2 Car Garage and additional 1000sf Detached Workshop. Private Well. Additional storage building or small workshop. Apple trees, Berries, Sales Shed out front. Room for horses, small orchard, garden, additional workshop. Excellent location for commuters. Fantastic find for a Home Run Business! Live up front and run your business out of the shop in back. Homestead or Hobby Farm! Value here! Move fast! $379,000
